# Thrift Store DB Design

## Problem
Design a database for a growing Instagram-based thrift + handmade store.

## ER Diagram
![ER Diagram](./diagram-export-4-6-2026-9_45_25-PM.png)

## Key Challenges
- Thrift items are unique (single quantity)
- Handmade items can have multiple units
- Orders can contain multiple products

## Design Decisions
- Used `order_items` to handle M:N relationship between orders and products
- Used `type` to distinguish thrift vs handmade
- Separated payment and delivery for flexibility

## Entities
- Customers
- Orders
- Order Items
- Stock
- Payments
- Delivery
